media:group.media:description:
HALO Trust has been working for almost three decades to clear Nagorno-Karabakh of landmines. HALO Trust has refocused its efforts since 2020 to clearing munitions and ordinances left over from that yearโs 44-day war. The team, mostly local Karabakh Armenians, also remains determined to educate locals about how to recognize and respond when they come across a mine.
